item.title: Skiing In Singapore
item.description: It is an online test provided by RedMart, who asks to solve a problem by using DFS algorithm. More details you can find here. Discription Sometimes it’s nice to take a break and code up a solution to a small, fun problem. Here is one some of our engineers enjoyed recently called Skiing In Singapore. Well you can’t really ski in Singapore. But let’s say you hopped on a flight to the Niseko ski resort in Japan.
